{"tid":1635571,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【煲大佢】教育局要求上報明天戴口罩學生數目","createTime":"2019-10-07T14:05:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T09:05:30.000Z","uid":204398,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"c41052bddf75ebfa562d34ef01422f933996c376","tid":1635571,"uid":204398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:05:44.000Z","msg":"政府上星期五（4日）實施《禁蒙面法》，明天（8日）學校長假期後開學，社會關注中學生會否戴上口罩表態。<br />\n中學校長會主席鄧振強出席一個電台節目時表示，教育局要求全港中學，明早11時之前通報戴口罩的學生數字，以及匯報有沒有學生叫口號和靜坐。<br />\n<br />\n仲有係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">強迫</span></span></strong>各間學校上報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講到明唔11點前唔上報就會親子去<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">詢問</span></span></strong>該學校校長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根本就係迫學校就範<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係教育局拎到個數字係想做啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你哋唔覺好大件事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">可能隨時抽後算帳呀</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30bf2cd1bc29dfc6c06c9437bcf2c0653acfdb0e","tid":1635571,"uid":331425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:06:22.000Z","msg":"可以點做？"},{"pid":"ae5aca5bc244a5da966f60f1fc10193e0c3bab46","tid":1635571,"uid":30453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:06:36.000Z","msg":"We are temporarily using live channel直播台as english channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634498\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634498</a><br />\n<br />\n[國際戰線] 連登開左英文台！English Channel is LIVE now on LIHKG!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634824\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634824</a>"},{"pid"